, {\"sentence\": \"Raisman's past made her understandably wary when it came to being alone with medics during her recent health scares.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raisman's past\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"medics\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"her recent health scares\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first time it happened was during COVID.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first time\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"COVID\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so, they would not let my mom in the ambulance with me,\\\" she recalled.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mom\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"the ambulance\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was aware enough to know, 'Oh my God, I have two men [with me], I can not move my arms and my legs, I can not move my body, I can not speak.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two men\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"my arms\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"my legs\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What if they take advantage of me?'\\\"\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"advantage\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was really still struggling a lot with PTSD,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"PTSD\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People do not realize how much it still lives with you when you have been through something traumatic.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 1996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, that was really hard for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The second episode happened a year and a half later, Raisman explained, and struck her with \\\"complete body paralysis\\\" that left her hospitalized for three days.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The second episode\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"Raisman\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"complete body paralysis\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"three days\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They would not release me because I could not sit up on my own.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It took me so long.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I needed help walking, going to the bathroom,\\\" she explained.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"the bathroom\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the most [difficult] to be able to go from being an athlete and being able to push myself so much to literally not even be able to move my fingers, move my legs.\\\"\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"my fingers\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"my legs\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the medical community, bouts of stroke-like symptoms are known as \\\"stroke mimics,\\\" and they have been linked to a series of potential causes including migraines, vertigo, and, commonly, functional neuro